## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and discussions, which may not encompass all perspectives or the latest developments in legal reforms. Additionally, some sources may reflect personal opinions rather than empirical evidence, which could influence the objectivity of the arguments presented. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.